	directAnswerHtml={`<strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">If you are a child, this is for you — God is your good, good Father.</strong> He made every part of you. He knows your name. He is never, ever too busy to listen. The <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Father's Heart Bible™</a> is a Bible you can read and <em>listen to</em> for free on any phone, and it has one big, happy secret on every page: God is a Father who loves you. When you are scared at night, when you feel sad, when you get in trouble — He is right there. You don't have to be the best or the smartest or the fastest. He loves you just because you are <em>you</em>.`}
