	painsHeading={`When kids feel scared or sad`}
	painsIntroHtml={`Every child feels worried or scared sometimes — of the dark, of a test, of being left alone, of not fitting in. That is normal, and it is okay. But more kids than ever are carrying big worries today, and they need to hear a gentle, true thing: you are not alone, and you are deeply loved.`}
	painStats={[
