	painsBodyHtml={`<p>If you ever feel scared, or worried, or like nobody understands — please know this: you are not the only one, and there is nothing wrong with you. Lots of kids feel that way. Even grown-ups feel that way.</p><p>And here is the best part. You were never meant to carry those big feelings all by yourself. You have a Father in heaven who is bigger than every fear, who is awake all night while you sleep, and who is holding you close even when you cannot see Him. When you feel scared, you can talk to Him — like talking to the kindest dad in the whole world. He always listens.</p>`}
