	aFatherHeading={`A Father just for you`}
	aFatherBodyHtml={`<p>Did you know that God is not far away, like a king on a tall throne who is too busy for little kids? God is a <strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">Father</strong> — and He is <em>your</em> Father. He wanted you. He made you on purpose. He picked your smile, your laugh, your eyes, and the sound of your voice.</p><p>A good father loves to be with his kids. He listens when they talk. He helps when they fall down. He says, "I'm so glad you're mine." That is what God is like — only even better. He never gets too tired. He never gets too busy. He is never far away.</p><p>So when you feel small, remember: you have the biggest, strongest, kindest Father in all of heaven. And He loves you more than you could ever count.</p>`}
