		{ heading: `It shows God as a loving Father`, bodyHtml: `Lots of Bibles call God "God." The Father's Heart Bible™ shows Him as a <em>Father</em> — a good, kind Dad who loves His children. From <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">the very first page</a>, kids meet a God who is gentle and close.` },
